# 🤖 AI Resume Analyzer

An AI-powered resume analysis tool that evaluates how well a resume matches a job description using Natural Language Processing (NLP) and cosine similarity.

Built with Python, Streamlit, spaCy, and Scikit-learn.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Resume vs Job Description matching
- TF-IDF vectorization
- Cosine similarity scoring
- Keyword extraction
- Missing keyword detection
- ATS-style recruiter feedback
- Clean interactive web interface (Streamlit)

---

## 🧠 How It Works

1. Text is cleaned and normalized.
2. Keywords are extracted using spaCy NLP.
3. TF-IDF vectorization converts text into numerical representations.
4. Cosine similarity measures alignment between resume and job description.
5. Missing keywords are identified to improve ATS compatibility.

---

## 📊 Example Output

- Match Score: 78%
- Missing Keywords: ["Docker", "Kubernetes", "CI/CD"]
- Recruiter Insight: Moderate match. Consider optimizing keywords.

---
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm
streamlit run app.py
